    {
        "content": "<p>chinhkrb113 opened <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/pull/13517\">PR #13517</a> from <code>chinhkrb113:improve/quality/re-export-jitmemorykind-from-the-crate-r</code> to <code>bytecodealliance:main</code>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<h2>Summary</h2>\n<p>Making <code>JITMemoryKind</code> public in <code>memory.rs</code> is not sufficient if it is not re-exported from the crate root alongside <code>JITMemoryProvider</code> and the other memory-related public items. Downstream users import these symbols from <code>cranelift_jit::...</code>, so the type needs to be reachable through the same path used for <code>JITMemoryProvider</code></p>\n<p>Fixes #13200</p>\n<h2>Changes</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><code>cranelift/jit/src/lib.rs</code></li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Why</h2>\n<p><code>cranelift/jit/src/lib.rs</code>: Making <code>JITMemoryKind</code> public in <code>memory.rs</code> is not sufficient if it is not re-exported from the crate root alongside <code>JITMemoryProvider</code> and the other memory-related public items. Downstream users import these symbols from <code>cranelift_jit::...</code>, so the type needs to be reachable through the same path used for <code>JITMemoryProvider</code>.<br>\n</p>\n</blockquote>",
